						<div class="postbody">As Disch says, there are no negative values. If you want to understand high-pass filtering, I highly recommend writing a separate program to get it working. It can be just a simple main() that generates a tone, applies the filter, then writes to a wave file. That will eliminate everything else as a possible cause, allowing you to focus on the filtering code.</div>

